('urn:li:lyndaVideo:(urn:li:lyndaCourse:756320,793445)', '2020-07-18T16:17:29.000Z', '{"urn":"urn:li:lyndaVideo:(urn:li:lyndaCourse:756320,793445)","title":{"value":"Understanding data security"},"details":{"urls":{"webLaunch":"https://www.linkedin.com/learning/cism-cert-prep-1-information-security-governance/understanding-data-security"},"images":{},"timeToComplete":{"duration":193},"descriptionIncludingHtml":{"value":"Data is often an organization’s most valuable asset. As such, it’s appropriate that information security professionals spend a large amount of their time ensuring the confidentiality, integrity, and availability of information assets. In this video, you can learn the concepts of data security, including securing data at rest and data in transit and how data security affects big data use."}}}'),
